~ start
These buttons aren't reachable...
Do you want some extra needles?
- Yes => help_accepted
- No => help_denied

~ help_accepted
do ExtraNeedles.add_extra_needles()
Bye!
do GameState.global.helper.clear()
=> END

~ help_denied
OK, bye!
=> END
